data.description: Welcome to your new home at 11418 Honeysuckle Ct. in Upper Marlboro, MD!  *** This home qualifies for a 100% financing option, ask the listing agent for details***  This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhouse is move-in ready and perfect for those who want to be close to all the action.  With its newly renovated kitchen and spacious living areas, this home is sure to please. Step inside and be greeted by a bright and airy living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. This chef's dream kitchen features stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and plenty of cabinet space for all your culinary needs. Upstairs, you'll find two spacious bedrooms that are well-appointed with ample closet space and natural light. This home is located in the desirable Upper Marlboro area, just minutes from shopping, dining, and entertainment options. It's also close to major highways, making it easy to commute to work or school. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this charming townhouse your own! Schedule a showing today and see everything this home has to offer.
